## Development

```bash
# Create virtual environment
hatch env create
# Activate virtual environment
hatch shell
# Run test
hatch run test
# Run lint
hatch run lint:style

# Version dump
hatch version patch/minor/major
# Build
hatch build
# Upload to pypi
hatch publish
```

